This paper discusses the DLV system, which is a tool for knowledge representation and reasoning. The paper covers topics such as formal definitions of logic programs, computational complexity, and applications. These topics are all related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), logic (cs.LO), databases (cs.DB), software engineering (cs.SE), and programming languages (cs.PL). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
